export default {

  Hanbetsu(studentId) {//学籍番号で分ける
        for (var i = 0; i <= this.count ; i++){
          this.a = this.studentId.slice( 0, 1 ) ;
          if(this.a == "s"){
            this.idS.push(this.users[i].studentId);
            this.counterS += 1;
          }else if(this.a == "m"){
            this.idM.push(this.users[i]);
          }else if(this.a == "a"){
            this.idA.push(this.users[i]);
          }else if(this.a == "k"){
            this.idK.push(this.users[i]);
          }else if(this.a == "b"){
            this.idB.push(this.users[i]);
          }else{
            this.idZ.push(this.users[i])
          }
        }
        this.Sort(this.idS);
        this.Sort(this.idM);
        this.Sort(this.idA);
        this.Sort(this.idB);
        this.Sort(this.idK);
        this.Sort(this.idZ);
      },
      Sort(a) {
        for(var i=0;i<a.length-1;i++){
          for(var j=a.length-1;j>i;j--){
	          if(a[j]<a[j-1]){
	            this.t=a[j];
	            a[j]=a[j-1];
	            a[j-1]=this.t;
	          }
          }
        }
      }
};
</script>
